dsDescriptionValue.value:
This dataset contains the images for 313 Swift/BAT selected AGN using the SPIRE instrument onboard the Herschel Space Observatory. For each source there are six FITS files which contain the signal (*_signal.fits) and error (*_error.fits) map at each waveband (250, 350, and 500 micron). 

If you find these images useful in your research, please cite the related publication.
